Common Questions
How do I restore my ad-free purchase?
Open the App, go to Settings, and tap "Restore Purchases." This will restore your remove-ads purchase if you've bought it previously on the same Apple ID.

My progress was lost. Can I get it back?
Game progress is saved locally on your device. If you deleted and reinstalled the App, local save data cannot be recovered. Your Game Center leaderboard score is preserved through your Apple ID.

The game is crashing or not loading.
Try closing the App completely and reopening it. If the issue persists, make sure you are running the latest version from the App Store. Restarting your device can also help.

How do I turn off ads?
You can purchase the one-time "Remove Ads" option from the in-game Store to permanently remove all ads.

